    <description>Lorena Ríos is a freelance journalist based in Turkey. She started her career in Egypt and has been reporting in the region for the last three years. She covers culture, food, displacement and human stories told against the backdrop of sociopolitical landscapes. Follow her on Twitter@rioslorena.
